text: Herrad Frey was an archer from France. He was born on 25 August 1933 and died on 19 November 2022. Frey competed at the 1972 Summer Olympic Games.Herrad FreyHerrad Frey == References == Category:1933 births Category:2022 deaths Category:French archers Category:Olympians for France
